文章编号：1005-8451（2019）4-0008-06
铁路大数据应用实践及展望
马小宁
（中国铁道科学研究院集团有限公司 铁路大数据研究与应用创新中心，北京 100081） 摘 要：大数据是新一轮科技革命的制高点，是全面贯彻落实铁路总公司智能铁路战略的有力抓 手。经过前期的积累，铁路大数据正处于全面深化应用的阶段。文章分析大数据的核心价值，介绍铁路 大数据应用的总体蓝图，剖析典型铁路局的大数据应用实践，总结存在的问题，并对未来工作进行展 望。该研究对于现阶段进一步理清大数据工作思路、把握铁路大数据发展方向具有积极意义。 关键词：铁路大数据；人工智能；铁路数据服务平台 中图分类号： U29∶TP39 文献标识码： A

Application practice and prospect of railway big data
MA Xiaoning
( Research and Application Innovation Center for Big Data Technology in Railway, China Academy of Railway Sciences Corporation Limited, Beijing  100081, China )
Abstract: Big data is the commanding height of a new round of scientific and technological revolution, which is a powerful grasp to fully implement the intelligent railway strategy of the China Railway. On the basis of the accumulation in the early stage, the railway big data is in the stage of deepening application. This paper analyzed the core value of big data, introduced the overall blueprint of big data application of railway, analyzed the big data application of the railway administration, summarized the existing problems and forecasted the future work. This research is significant in further clarifying the working ideas and grasping the development direction of railway big data. Keywords: railway big data; artificial intelligence; railway data service platform

